<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Message Received</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #2d3436; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #f0f4f0; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f 0%, #52b788 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
      .header .icon { font-size: 42px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .content { background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; }
      .greeting { font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #2d3436; }
      .body-text { color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 15px; }
      .summary { background: #f8faf8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #d8e8d8; }
      .summary-title { font-weight: 700; color: #2d6a4f; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .field { margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .field-label { font-weight: 700; color: #2d6a4f; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
      .field-value { color: #2d3436; margin-top: 3px; }
      .message-box { background: #f0f4f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 6px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; border-left: 3px solid #52b788; }
      .info-box { background: #fff8f0; border-left: 4px solid #f4a261; padding: 14px 16px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 6px; color: #6b4226; font-size: 14px; }
      .signature { margin-top: 24px; color: #555; font-size: 15px; }
      .signature strong { color: #2d6a4f; }
      .footer { background: #1b4332; color: #95d5b2; padding: 18px; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; }
      .footer p { margin: 4px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">✓</div>
      <h1>Message Received!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</div>
      <p class="body-text">
        We have received your message and thank you for contacting us.
        Our team will review it and get back to you as soon as possible.
      </p>
      <div class="summary">
        <div class="summary-title">Summary</div>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="field-label">Subject</div>
          <div class="field-value">{{subject}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="field-label">Date Received</div>
          <div class="field-value">{{timestamp}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="field-label">Your Message</div>
          <div class="message-box">{{message}}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        If you have any other questions or if your request is urgent, please don't hesitate to contact us again.
      </div>
      <div class="signature">
        Best regards,<br /><strong>{{companyName}}</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent automatically, please do not reply.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
